Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.91,0:45:12.12,EDRomanji,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.12,0:45:24.32,EDRomanji,,0010,0010,0000,,{\kf156}nagai {\kf79}yoru {\kf143}ga {\kf59}asa {\kf86}ga {\kf43}hiru {\kf100}ga {\kf69}subete {\kf214}norarikurari {\kf190}nagare {\kf40}yuku {\kf41}yo
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.12,0:45:18.63,EDTL,,0000,0000,0000,,A longa noite, a manhã, a luz do dia
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.63,0:45:24.32,EDTL,,0000,0000,0000,,continuam passando por mim...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.18,0:45:36.94,EDRomanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\kf78}hibi {\kf74}wo {\kf171}tsunaide {\kf69}yuku {\kf121}nimo {\kf76}sou {\kf39}ne {\kf86}ishi {\kf51}to {\kf64}iu {\kf57}mono {\kf51}ga {\kf239}hitsuyou?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.18,0:45:30.76,EDTL,,0000,0000,0000,,E todos os dias estão se conectando.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.76,0:45:36.94,EDTL,,0000,0000,0000,,Então, ter uma meta é mesmo necessária?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.48,0:45:44.57,EDRomanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\kf136}kizutsuite {\kf161}naiteita {\kf45}hi {\kf33}mo {\kf65}atta {\kf33}ki {\kf36}ga {\kf100}suru
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.48,0:45:44.57,EDTL,,0000,0000,0000,,Eu sei que existem dias em que me machuco e choro
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.78,0:45:50.16,EDRomanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\kf116}nanika {\kf83}wo {\kf124}shinjiyou {\kf215}toshite
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.78,0:45:50.16,EDTL,,0000,0000,0000,,Mas, mesmo assim, eu tento acreditar no futuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.58,0:45:57.42,EDRomanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\kf172}sekai {\kf108}wa {\kf100}mawaru {\kf31}to {\kf29}yuu {\kf144}keredo
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.58,0:45:57.42,EDTL,,0000,0000,0000,,Mesmo que digam que o mundo continua girando,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.67,0:46:03.80,EDRomanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\kf111}nanimo {\kf60}watashi {\kf20}no {\kf34}naka {\kf75}meguru {\kf78}mono {\kf43}nado {\kf22}nai {\kf170}kara
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.67,0:46:03.80,EDTL,,0000,0000,0000,,Não existe nenhuma convicção em meu interior.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.80,0:46:10.35,EDRomanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\kf111}sotto {\kf154}tada {\kf88}mado {\kf31}no {\kf38}soto {\kf133}nagame
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.80,0:46:10.35,EDTL,,0000,0000,0000,,Deixe-me apenas contemplar a vista da janela silenciosamente,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.81,0:46:17.56,EDRomanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}{\kf96}kisetsu {\kf29}ga {\kf87}utsurou {\kf32}no {\kf79}wo {\kf352}miteimashou
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.81,0:46:17.56,EDTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}e observar as mudanças de estações.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.41,0:46:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ei, Hattori-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.46,0:46:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deixe-me ver seu ferimento.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.42,0:46:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O que é isso, de repente?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.92,0:46:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Você sabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.92,0:46:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Estou falando do ferimento de amor\N que a Kazuha-chan fez em você!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.55,0:46:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Não, Ran-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.05,0:46:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, aquele...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.05,0:46:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ele já estava completamente\N curado quando acordei.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.10,0:46:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Não pode ser...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.02,0:46:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eu deveria ter usado mais força.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.81,0:46:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Como assim, sua mala?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.61,0:47:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mas, ainda bem que já está curado.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.69,0:47:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquela flecha causou a morte de muitos, mas ficamos ilesos.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.20,0:47:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ei, Kazuha-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.41,0:47:10.07,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Tola.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.03,0:47:12.33,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Você é muito ingênua.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.62,0:47:15.12,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Eu nunca...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.12,0:47:17.08,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Nunca...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.87,0:47:20.21,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}deixaria você se ferir.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.21,0:47:25.92,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Seu carinha maneiro!
